      • removeTerms

        public static SalesforceField removeTerms​(java.lang.String qualifiedName,
                                          java.util.List<GlossaryTerm> terms)
                                   throws AtlanException
        Remove terms from a SalesforceField, without replacing all existing terms linked to the SalesforceField. Note: this operation must make two API calls one to retrieve the SalesforceField's existing terms, and a second to remove the provided terms.
        Parameters:
        qualifiedName - for the SalesforceField
        terms - the list of terms to remove from the SalesforceField, which must be referenced by GUID
        Returns:
        the SalesforceField that was updated (note that it will NOT contain details of the resulting terms)
        Throws:
        AtlanException - on any API problems
